{"tid":1233713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警告！」一堆中共間諜出現","createTime":"2019-06-16T20:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T21:09:08.000Z","uid":28963,"like":16,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2705f0c64dd5f86bf0f6b1c050da2ca8c3ae2f43","tid":1233713,"uid":28963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:41:07.000Z","msg":"今晚留守，龍和封路....都係為明天做準備，去畀壓力政府回應。大家要記得我哋仲係「零」戰果：<br />\n<br />\n撤回、下台、放人、追究黑警<br />\n而家係一樣都未有<br />\n<br />\n千祈唔好畀班間諜控制風向，話乜撚贏晒民意，唔好前功盡廢....全部都係廢話！<br />\n乜撚都未爭取到有咩可以輸？<br />\n<br />\n而家要做嘅喺文宣，要話俾「政治冷感」但又有出嚟嘅人知，林鄭個道歉新聞稿同冇講過嘢一樣，我哋要嘅嘢一樣都未有！<br />\n大家多啲宣傳呢個意識出去！等大家知道6.16到而家都仲係白行！"},{"pid":"d889f5f0b6b3bbd77e3820ecaf92d3303b7a1bce","tid":1233713,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:41:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"97cd8754088f37cec3d619840d779f410e82eecd","tid":1233713,"uid":28963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:42:43.000Z","msg":"大家可以搵返巴打分析林鄭道歉新聞張圖，大大力share出去畀更多人睇到林鄭係幾咁冇誠意！"},{"pid":"9c641754908b1154fcdd2b5c290ab8e409c9bff4","tid":1233713,"uid":28963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:44:07.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ec5d18fa51deb08f5cd05d2e52cab2de555bc7","tid":1233713,"uid":28963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c641754908b1154fcdd2b5c290ab8e409c9bff4","tid":1233713,"uid":28963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:44:07.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:44:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0da56860d7adb36fa40a9fe33f567914556ef014","tid":1233713,"uid":95679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T20:46:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab8b48979ca8c83d2fbd6c7d6f3b47bebf0aa927","tid":1233713,"uid":28963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"